about.summary: A Jekyll plugin to generate an Atom feed of your Jekyll posts

name: rb-jekyll-feed
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "jekyll-feed" %}
{% set version = "0.12.1" %}

package:
  name: rb-{{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://rubygems.org/downloads/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.gem
  sha256: e3514d6fb1529a685f36d3260dcfa2f51f1fd53592229b604b0c8fdce48ec005

build:
  noarch: generic
  number: 0
  script:
    - gem install -N -l -V --norc --ignore-dependencies {{ name }}-{{ version }}.gem
    - gem unpack {{ name }}-{{ version }}.gem
  skip: {{ win }}

requirements:
  host:
    - ruby
  run:
    - ruby
    - rb-jekyll >=3.7,<4.0

test:
  commands:
    - ruby -r {{ name }} -e 'exit 0'

about:
  home: https://rubygems.org/gems/{{ name }}
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: {{ name }}-{{ version }}/LICENSE.txt
  summary: A Jekyll plugin to generate an Atom feed of your Jekyll posts

  doc_url: https://www.rubydoc.info/gems/{{ name }}
  dev_url: https://github.com/jekyll/{{ name }}

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - sodre
